Text: RE The new democratic sealone beer what a wussy I thought you liked Becks I hope this is something that you wanted if so excellent I was looking forward to working on some long term stuff with you Keep me posted on the job Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday December AM To Subject RE The new democratic seal Go W Hey I know that Paul Choi called you this morning about Mona I just wanted to let you know that there is a probobility that I will be going back to Houston to market gas in the west I am very sad to leave Portland if it happens I will keep you posted but since things havent quite been announced please keep me off of your gossip vine until further notice If this takes place we must have one more beer Kim
